            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="sg">
          <div class="addons-note si">
            <span style="font-size:1.1rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px">💡</span
            >
            <p>
              <strong>Add-ons work with both pricing models.</strong> Hourly bookings:
              extras are typically handled within the booked time where possible.
              Flat rate bookings: extras are priced individually and added to your
              flat rate total. All prices confirmed at checkout.
